Building on Mac

- install g++, git, and homebrew
- `brew install portaudio`
- `git submodule update --init --recursive`
- `./build-mac.sh`
- `./client`

Building on Linux

- install Portaudio, g++, git, and make using your package manager
- `git submodule update --init --recursive`
- `make client`
- `./client`

Building on Windows

- good luck you're on your own

